                    { id: 20, text: 'What is the Trace of a matrix?', options: ['Sum of all elements', 'Product of diagonal elements', 'Sum of elements on the principal diagonal', 'Inverse of determinant'], correctAnswer: 2, explanation: 'The trace is the sum of the elements along the main diagonal from top-left to bottom-right.' }
